<p>The learning moments that comprise Paths, we're calling Prompts. To maximize retention, each user of the app is able to set a preference for how frequently they receive new Prompts. While there is currently a "constant" option to facilitate testing, the suggested frequencies range from one Prompt per day to one Prompt per month, and the default option is three Prompts per week.</p>

<p>We're calling the pieces that comprise a single Prompt, Segments. An individual Segment might be a message with an image or links, suggested exercises for the user to try, or a multiple choice question.</p>
